         2. Save important findings as notes using the save_note tool.
         3. After gathering enough information, read your notes and produce a
            well-structured summary with key findings and sources.
         Be thorough but concise. Use at least 3 different search queries.
         """,
     name: "ResearchAgent",
     description: "An agent that researches topics by searching the web and taking notes.",
     tools: tools);

 // ── Run ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 Console.WriteLine("╔══════════════════════════════════════════╗");
